1 and others of record interested in [said] THE abutting property of a hearing at which they
2 will be given an opportunity to be heard[, such].
3 (5) THE hearing [to be had] SHALL BE before [said Drummond Citizens’
4 Committee] THE VILLAGE COUNCIL, which shall decide the matters properly brought
