8 65–13.
9 IF ANY SECTION OR PART OF A SECTION OF THIS CHAPTER IS HELD INVALID
10 BY A COURT OF COMPETENT JURISDICTION, THE HOLDING MAY NOT AFFECT THE
11 REMAINDER OF THIS CHAPTER NOR THE CONTEXT IN WHICH THE SECTION OR PART
12 OF THE SECTION HELD INVALID APPEARS, EXCEPT TO THE EXTENT THAT AN ENTIRE
13 SECTION OR PART OF A SECTION MAY BE INSEPARABLY CONNECTED IN MEANING
14 AND EFFECT WITH THE SECTION OR PART OF THE SECTION TO WHICH THE HOLDING
15 DIRECTLY APPLIES.
16 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
17 October 1, 2026.
